Buoc 1: Cai trinh bien dich gcc, make, automake, autoconf va thu vien ncurses 

Debian/Ubuntu 18.04
apt -y install gcc make automake autoconf libncurses5-dev

RHEL/CentOS 7
yum -y install gcc make automake autoconf ncurses-devel

Buoc 2: Cai tu ma nguon (source code)

autoreconf -iv

./configure

---Tao cac target cho make vi du make check | clean | mostlyclean...

make 

---Cai ung dung bang make

make install

---Co the ket hop 2 lenh lai nhu sau

make && make install

Buoc 3: Chay chuong trinh

chaoban

---Xem trang huong dan (manpage)

man chaoban

---Gom cac file ma nguon cua ung dung thanh 1 file .tar.gz

make dist

---Xem noi dung file .tar.gz

tar -ztf chaoban-0.9.tar.gz

---Tra ve ma nguon (source code) ban dau sau khi chay lenh make install

make maintainer-clean